パッケージ ch.uzh.ifi.seal.changedistiller.treedifferencing.matching.measure

  • インタフェースの概要 
    インタフェース 説明
    NodeSimilarityCalculator
    Interface for (inner) node similarity calculators.
    StringSimilarityCalculator
    Interface for string similarity calculators.
  • クラスの概要 
    クラス 説明
    ChawatheCalculator
    Implementation of the default inner node similarity calculator proposed by Chawathe.
    LevenshteinSimilarityCalculator
    Implementation of a StringSimilarityCalculator based on the Levenshtein distance.
    NGramsCalculator
    Implementation of the ngrams similarity measure.
    TokenBasedCalculator
    Implementation of a token based string similarity calculator.
